{
  "stem": "523.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody knows what from minute to minute happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because actual the Allies, the D-Day started only June, '44.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were home already by then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it's-- I think the feeling home, to go home, it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So no matter what, we just wanted to go home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're marching home from town to town, from town to town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we came to Bessarabia, when we marched to Transnistria, the villager were throwing stones at us and screaming at us, and just how.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we came back, suddenly they became good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember once, it was-- it must have been Easter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because you know, the Romanian Christian are Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they color their eggs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they brought us the Easter eggs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But when we marched to Transnistria, nobody gave us anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But when we came back, unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were marching every day 35, 40 kilometer from point A to point B, sleeping cover overnight.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- whereverit was place to sleepover, to have rest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now when people say, I have to go to the shopping, they you need the car?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were walking 35, 30, 35 kilometer a day after almost three years of concentration camp, of Transnistria, of hunger, of starvation.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many times I think, where did we get the energy?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where did we get the strength to march back in a such a condition?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Me and my brother, a lot of people, I still were wrapped up in rugs because we didn't have any clothes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was, when we arrived-- How long was the journey from [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Brest ?] back to Ediniti?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Has to have been a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who counted?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It just was such a time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's impossible.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
